Name: SERIAL LETTER
Explanation: AN ALPHABETIC CHARACTER IDENTIFYING AN INDIVIDUAL COMMUNICATION.

Name: REFERENCE SET SERIAL LETTER
Explanation: THE SERIAL LETTER IN FF-SQ 1 OF THE REFERENCE SET OF A FORMATTED MESSAGE.

Name: TRANSPORTATION REQUIREMENT IDENTIFIER
Explanation: THE NAME OR DESIGNATION USED TO IDENTIFY A NEED FOR TRANSPORTING MATERIALS AND EQUIPMENT.

Name: PROJECT, REPORT OR MESSAGE IDENTIFIER
Explanation: A UNIQUE 2-LETTER CODE GENERATED BY THE ORIGINATOR OF THE PROJECT, REPORT OR MESSAGE.

Name: BEACON ID LETTER
Explanation: THE LETTER THAT IDENTIFIES THE BEACON BEING REPORTED.

Name: AEW SORTIE NUMBER SERIAL IDENTIFIER
Explanation: A SERIAL IDENTIFIER IN THE RANGE [AA, AB THROUGH ZZ], USED TO IDENTIFY AN AEW SORTIE NUMBER.

Name: SUBFORSUM SERIAL NUMBER
Explanation: SUBMARINE FORCES SUMMARY MESSAGE SERIAL NUMBER.
